{"tid":2243592,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"其實陳偉霆根本冇咩問題，笑佢既香港人都係跟風狗","createTime":"2020-10-15T00:36:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-18T02:36:14.000Z","uid":353419,"like":9,"dislike":126,"uniUserReply":34,"replies":[{"pid":"371729de7f023fef49873013ee3198d9b715f56b","tid":2243592,"uid":353419,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T00:36:54.000Z","msg":"佢本身講野又唔黑人憎, 又咩做啲咩衰野,<br />\n就係因為一句'而我不知道陳偉霆是誰&quot; 就笑9佢,<br />\n唔明有咩好笑,黃曉明知佢係舊菜,所以先咁講姐.<br />\n<br />\n好多人笑陳偉霆英皇比賽跳舞核突, 但我睇到係佢既進步,<br />\n佢08年單飛果陣,跳舞唔可以話勁(我睇開MJ) ,但都叫正正常常,<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0sUyTnUddPs\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0sUyTnUddPs&h=d85306f9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n佢演技可能好差, 但有觀眾緣,賺錢賺到發笑<br />\n<br />\n退一萬步,即使佢跳舞柒, 演技差,<br />\n唔明香港人哪來自信笑佢, 比起張國榮,佢遠遠唔夠靚仔,<br />\n但對比普通港男港女, 佢一定靚仔過大家勁多,<br />\n靜係個樣,佢都嬴左啦<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3yYkpdh.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3yYkpdh.png&h=e41a341a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"b9676a852e70ea0ddae9b7f6a38cbad752b6f12f","tid":2243592,"uid":353419,"like":1,"dislike":14,"score":-13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T00:37:13.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0sUyTnUddPs\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3D0sUyTnUddPs&d=LQfwTnO421PZAKP%2FvRgyie6cow1LS9WQT%2BeJ8I%2F17x8%3D&h=5ea2a3de\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=0sUyTnUddPs</a>"},{"pid":"f57dcdc8f4ae0fd7612d4e05210b3b5ce513e5c2","tid":2243592,"uid":104218,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T00:39:24.000Z","msg":"的士佬<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/solution.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e2d7f8874b4bbefab213255fcb2a8ec254da31e3","tid":2243592,"uid":228143,"like":7,"dislike":6,"score":1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2020-10-15T00:39:51.000Z","msg":"冇笑喎 <br />\n<br />\n不過d人吹捧佢紅先搞笑者<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sos